pageContext.claim: “The Great State of North Carolina has EARLY VOTING for a very important Congressional (Ninth) race. Please vote early (now), or on Election Day, September 10th, for Dan Bishop, a great guy. His opponent wants Open Borders, Sanctuary Cities & is weak on Crime, Military & Vets!”
pageContext.analysis: The Democratic candidate, Dan McCready, is a former Marine captain who deployed to Iraq and pledged to support veterans. He also favored stronger border controls.
